- type = @geographies.first.type

%h1 #{type.capitalize} Snapshots
%h3.page-header Regional Trends and Current Conditions

.break

.row
  .col-xs-12
    .geography-selector
    = render partial: 'select', locals: {type: type, selected: nil}

.row
  .col-xs-12
    %p
      Community Snapshots are a quick and easy way to access basic information about a #{type}. The snapshots pull together a wide range of data on each #{type}, and are a great place to start investigating what data we have available.